OL,3,CTeen found guilty of murdering dad-of-
OL,4,Cseven after street argument
OL,6,FA teenager has been found guilty of
OL,7,Fmurdering a father-of-seven who was
OL,8,Fstabbed to death in the street
OL,9,Ffollowing an argument between a former
OL,10,Fcouple.
OL,12,FColin Richards died within minutes
OL,13,Fafter sustaining a stab wound to the
OL,14,Ftop of his right thigh just after 11pm
OL,15,Fon April 7 last year.
OL,17,FCorey Gauci, 19, stabbed Mr Richards,
OL,18,F48, in the leg, leaving him to bleed
OL,19,Fto death. He suffered damage to the
OL,20,Ffemoral artery and vein ` an injury
OL,21,Fwhich proved to be fatal.
