OL,3,CTeen found guilty of murdering dad-of-
OL,4,Cseven after street argument
OL,6,FGauci had become involved in an
OL,7,Fargument between former couple Noreen
OL,8,FO'Driscoll and Christian Morgan, which
OL,9,Fsaw two groups travelling to an area
OL,10,Fof Ely in Cardiff, some armed with
OL,11,Fknives.
OL,13,FFollowing a trial at Cardiff Crown
OL,14,FCourt, a jury returned verdicts in
OL,15,Frespect of Gauci, of Wilson Road, Ely,
OL,16,Fwho was found guilty of murder and
OL,17,Fviolent disorder on Wednesday, 9 April.
OL,19,FHe is due to be sentenced at a later
OL,20,Fdate.
